# Filament Upgrade

## When to use

- Upgrading Filament v3 to v4
- Upgrading Filament v4 to v5
- Handling Tailwind v4 migration required by Filament 4+
- Handling Livewire v4 migration required by Filament 5
- Resolving Filament breaking changes after upgrade

## Keywords

`filament upgrade`, `filament v3 to v4`, `filament v4 to v5`, `filament migration`, `filament breaking changes`, `filament update`
